table.name: countries
table.Comment: This table holds the duty country. It will be used to calculate taxation tables

table.name: edstypes
table.Comment: This table holds the types of earnings and deductions that are available in country

table.name: recurrents
table.Comment: This table holds the values of "YES" or "NO"

column.name: recurrent_id
column.Comment: This table holds the value of a yes or No, to determine if an earning, deduction etc value is repeated or should be continously captured.

column.name: taxable_id
column.Comment: This are values of the tax state of earn, deduction etc. It takes Yes or No

column.name: description
column.Comment: Description of the payroll center. Which category of people does it apply to?
